Class RDFQuery

java.lang.Object
  org.obd.model.bridge.RDFQuery

public class RDFQuery
extends java.lang.Object

Lightweight query object for representing a query over an RDF model that can be translated to SPARQL. Has methods for translating from an OBD query object SPARQL Examples
